{"id":606682,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/【cdtv】天下手机谁最美？大家都说是华为/","date":"2019-02-27T17:11:18Z","modified":"2019-02-28T05:49:28Z","title":"【CDTV】儿歌《华为美》：天下手机谁最美？大家都说是华为","content":"<p>据新浪科技报道，今日微博一则《华为美》的歌曲MV引发极大关注。华为官方官微@花粉俱乐部 对此回应称，这部作品是在华为不知情、未参与的情况下由网友自发创作。然而，有网友检索词曲作者信息发现，疑似其均具有中共官方背景。</p>\n<p><iframe width=\"600\" height=\"338\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/c0tvr5ETVdE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>视频由众多小朋友拍摄而成，主要内容是宣扬“国产手机要爱华为”，歌词中多次出现“爱祖国”、“新时代”、“为国争光”等。该视频来源被标注为：珠海市青少年妇女儿童活动中心周丹少儿声乐教室</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/OqQr-htptaqf3034449.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606684\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/OqQr-htptaqf3034449.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"232\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/OqQr-htptaqf3034449.jpg 583w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/OqQr-htptaqf3034449-300x127.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>《华为美》词曲如图</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/d_Jw-htptaqf3063501.png\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606685\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/d_Jw-htptaqf3063501.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"709\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/d_Jw-htptaqf3063501.png 587w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/d_Jw-htptaqf3063501-233x300.png 233w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 550px) 100vw, 550px\" /></a></p>\n<p>从微博网友的<a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/1638782947/HiDSsaamK?type=comment#_rnd1551287067317\">评论</a>看，不少网友认为，若此举出自华为，是极其低级的爱国营销，若真出自网友之手，则是非常低劣的“捧杀”，浓浓的“朝鲜风格”，把国家、政治、爱国、洗脑教育相互捆绑，显得极其怪异。Global Times也对此进行了报道转发，有网友评论称这也许有助于我们理解“华为是一家私企”的全部意涵。</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">How Chinese residents show their support to <a href=\"https://twitter.com/hashtag/Huawei?src=hash&amp;ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">#Huawei</a>? Singing! A video &quot;Huawei Beauty&quot; which features children singing lyrics supporting Huawei went viral. Lyrics include &quot;we love our country, we love homegrown brand Huawei&quot; and &quot;China’s homegrown chips are the most valuable one.&quot; <a href=\"https://t.co/kx5sUGV5Qs\">pic.twitter.com/kx5sUGV5Qs</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; Global Times (@globaltimesnews) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/globaltimesnews/status/1100675654746402816?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 27, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/IMG_5804.jpg\"><img class=\"aligncenter wp-image-606683\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/IMG_5804.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"798\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/IMG_5804.jpg 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/IMG_5804-169x300.jpg 169w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/IMG_5804-577x1024.jpg 577w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a></p>\n<p>网友变态辣椒：我搜索出的词曲作者信息</p>\n<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\" data-width=\"550\" data-dnt=\"true\">\n<p lang=\"zh\" dir=\"ltr\">华为官微回应称，这部作品是在华为不知情、未参与的情况下由网友自发创作。我搜索此歌詞曲作者信息如下：李幼容，总政歌舞团词作家，享受国务院政府津贴待遇。臧思佳，辽宁公安边防民警，公安文联会员、作家。郑冷横，国务院“政府特殊津贴的专家”、湖南音协音乐教育委员会副会长、岳阳市政协常委。 <a href=\"https://t.co/RIXkTBGifh\">https://t.co/RIXkTBGifh</a></p>\n<p>&mdash; 变态辣椒 (@remonwangxt) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/remonwangxt/status/1100831747384721408?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">February 27, 2019</a></p></blockquote>\n<p><script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读：中国数字空间 | <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%8D%8E%E4%B8%BA\">华为</a